Map Sample


This document shows two examples of mapping in R. Data is pulled directly from the Census ACS API and mapped below as both static and dynamic examples. There are many different way that these outputs can be adjusted. Furthermore, it is possible to publish the interactive version to the internet, embedding in future content.

Source: U.S. Census Bureau, American Community Survey (ACS) 5-Year Estimates, 2014-2018.
